{"tid":788092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"王宗堯爆Jessica＠SG被封「呻吟界C朗」","createTime":"2018-08-21T08:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T11:19:08.000Z","uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"2787b120ddf5d8fba8326cd951c41e9b4d36bba8","tid":788092,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180821/photo/bkn-20180821132631652-0821_00862_001_01p.jpg?20180821145351\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180821%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180821132631652-0821_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20180821145351&h=1fa84df2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王宗堯（左圖）大爆Jessica畀人笑天生識呻吟。<br />\n<br />\n藝人王宗堯到電台宣傳網劇《向西聞記之碌架床》，劇中他與蔡明思（Jessica＠Super Girls）有床戲，他透露Jessica為此練習呻吟，卻被戲稱為「呻吟界C朗」，他說：「佢畀人笑天生叻，所以唔使練，好似球星C朗咁邊使練波㗎？咁樣畀人笑但明明又唔關佢事。」<br />\n<br />\n他又指劇中演其父親的林雪有不少出位演出，除了與Jessica亦有床戲外，更會在客廳「大解」，直言劇情好荒誕。他又笑指林雪經常爆肚：「每個Take啲粗口都唔同咗，有啲甚至係寫唔出㗎。」"},{"pid":"95d23c345d5d9c3a78a28f5378afbc775fa1a62c","tid":788092,"uid":161592,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"咁都帶到落牙朗拿度 痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e21de0334182368419b10cdc4b684814e569b3","tid":788092,"uid":186784,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:37:15.000Z","msg":"有邊條女天生唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左啞既之外"},{"pid":"1fc3720ba2383c9081e481be4218a36ea454fab6","tid":788092,"uid":21275,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:46:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b9ebe93acc7f2b57838ada940572390068d0555","tid":788092,"uid":5549,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣食好多靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de56f84ef516d5733af6517014cfcf7f0cc2a00c","tid":788092,"uid":54373,"like":3,"